at":"2013-10-22t17:05:29z","body":"we need a config switch for that. you want to count the shared folder sometimes and sometimes not. "},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/27753917","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2796#issuecomment-27753917","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2796","id":27753917,"user":{"login":"pvince81","id":277525,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e446b529679416eb70eafb4ca4da5bbe?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f89d7c394e6dcdf87a91c75ac3b2ccbe8.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"e446b529679416eb70eafb4ca4da5bbe","url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81","html_url":"https://github.com/pvince81","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-11-05t08:16:51z","updated_at":"2013-11-05t08:16:51z","body":"which one is the most common use case ?\r\n\r\ni think it shouldn't be possible for people to \"pollute\" your storage.\r\n\r\nalso, if user1 has 1 gb quota and user2 has 1 gb quota, and the total hard disk space is 2 gb. currently if user2 shares 1 gb with user1, user1 won't be able to upload anything, which means that 1 gb hard disk space will be available forever, wasted.\r\n\r\ncan we make the \"not counting /shared\" in a user's quota the default ? the switch (if easy to add) will switch it back to the current behavior.\r\n\r\ni'll have a look how difficult it is to implement as it is affecting another fix of mine.\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/27755205","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2796#issuecomment-27755205","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2796","id":27755205,"user":{"login":"pvince81","id":277525,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e446b529679416eb70eafb4ca4da5bbe?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f89d7c394e6dcdf87a91c75ac3b2ccbe8.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"e446b529679416eb70eafb4ca4da5bbe","url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81","html_url":"https://github.com/pvince81","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-11-05t08:45:08z","updated_at":"2013-11-05t08:45:08z","body":"i just had a try with oc 6 beta 2 (master) and it seems shared files aren't counted in the actual quota.\r\nbut whatever is displayed in the ui is wrong.\r\n\r\nsteps:\r\n1. create two users, user1 and user2 and set their quota to 100 mb\r\n2. login as user1, upload a 90 mb file\r\n3. share the file with user2\r\n4. login as user2\r\n5. upload a 50 mb file\r\n6. upload a 60 mb file\r\n\r\nat step 5, the file goes through.\r\nat step 6, it doesn't since 50+60 > 100 mb.\r\nthe 90 mb file that is in the shared dir didn't count.\r\n\r\nwhich means this seems to be fixed already in oc6 but the ui needs to be fixed to show the correct values, there's a pr for that already: https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/5399\r\n\r\ncan someone confirm this ?\r\n\r\n\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/27758324","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2796#issuecomment-27758324","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2796","id":27758324,"user":{"login":"pvince81","id":277525,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/e446b529679416eb70eafb4ca4da5bbe?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f89d7c394e6dcdf87a91c75ac3b2ccbe8.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"e446b529679416eb70eafb4ca4da5bbe","url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81","html_url":"https://github.com/pvince81","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/pvince81/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-11-05t09:42:04z","updated_at":"2013-11-25t22:57:20z","body":"i've done some tests to try and check all use cases and see whether they work consistently with the idea that the file/dir owner is the one whose quota is affected.\r\n\r\n### case a: regular quota without sharing.\r\n\r\n:white_check_mark: works\r\n\r\n### case b: file sharing\r\n\r\nuser1 shares file f with user2.\r\nsize of file f counts in user1's quota.\r\n\r\n:white_check_mark: works in oc6.\r\n\r\n### case c: shared dir with write permissions\r\n\r\nuser1 shares directory d with user2.\r\nuser2 uploads file f into directory.\r\n\r\n:white_check_mark: works in oc6 beta 5\r\nraised as https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/5697\r\n\r\n### case d: public dir with write permissions\r\n\r\nuser1 shared directory d with public link, with upload enabled.\r\nexternal user uploads file f into d using the public link.\r\n\r\n:white_check_mark: works in oc6: the file f is counted against user1's quota.\r\ncan't upload a file that would exceed the quota.\r\n\r\n### case e: total used space shown in files list\r\n\r\n:white_check_mark: works correctly in oc6. was fixed by pr https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/5399\r\n\r\n### case f: total used space shown in personal page\r\n\r\n:white_check_mark: works correcly in oc6 beta 5. fixed by  https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/5927\r\n\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/27781299","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2796#issuecomment-27781299","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2796","id":27781299,"user":{"login":"frisco82","id":487098,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/a20ee2cef4622e8a67d9402ecb367f4b?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fa7abc00a60c19610dde8abf077f754e8.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"a20ee2cef4622e8a67d9402ecb367f4b","url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82","html_url":"https://github.com/frisco82","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/frisco82/r